              'GDMT for HFrEF includes: ACEi/ARB/ARNI (reduce afterload, prevent remodeling), beta-blockers (reduce heart rate, reverse remodeling), MRA (block aldosterone effects), SGLT2i (reduce preload, cardioprotection).',
