        'In men and postmenopausal women, assume GI blood loss until proven otherwise',
        'Do not start iron until you have a plan to find the cause',
        'Check reticulocyte count at 1-2 weeks to assess response to therapy',
        'Pica (especially ice craving) is highly suggestive of iron deficiency',
